se.  There is no cost to you and remember it’s only about an hour of your time.  After watching the videos you’ll need to take the 25 question quiz on the training page.  Once you pass, you’ll be emailed a certificate of completion.  Southeast will also be notified of your completion of the training.  Only volunteers 18 years of age or older will be required to take this training.</p> {% endif %} <table width=""100%"" border=""0"" cellspacing=""0"" cellpadding=""0"">   <tr>     <td align=""center"">       <div>         <!--[if mso]>           <v:roundrect xmlns:v=""urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml"" xmlns:w=""urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word"" href=""{{ Workflow | Attribute: ""MinistrySafeURL""}}"" style=""height:36px;v-text-anchor:middle;width:450px;"" arcsize=""5%"" strokecolor=""#31b0d5"" fillcolor=""#31b0d5"">             <w:anchorlock/>             <center style=""color:#ffffff;font-family:Helvetica, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;"">Start MinistrySafe &rarr;</center>           </v:roundrect>         <![endif]-->         <a href=""{{ Workflow | Attribute: ""MinistrySafeURL""}}"" style=""background-color:#31b0d5;border:1px solid #31b0d5;border-radius:3px;color:#ffffff;display:inline-block;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:44px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;width:450px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;mso-hide:all;"">Start MinistrySafe &rarr;</a>       </div>     </td>   </tr> </table>  <br /> <br />  {{ 'Global' | Attribute:'EmailFooter' }}  " ); // MinistrySafe:Start:Send the Email:Body
